henderson, ky cynthia richard march 21, 1954 - june 6, 2015 send card cynthia joyce richard 61 of henderson passed away june 6, 2015 at redbanks nursing home.
she was born march 21, 1954 in new bedford, massachusetts.
she was a sales associate at wal mart and of the catholic faith.
she is survived by her husband: calix richard. 2 children: michelle king of henderson.
